title: Supreme Court, in 5-4 Vote, Restores Alabama’s Congressional Voting Map - The New York Times
content: Supreme Court, in 5-4 Vote, Restores Alabama’s Congressional Voting Map  The New York TimesView Full Coverage on Google News
description: A special three-judge court had ordered lawmakers to redraw the lines, saying Black voters “have less opportunity” than other Alabamians to elect their favored candidates.
